  "title": "An Audience With Lord Juuka",
  "summary": "A masked, black-clad stranger calling himself Vidious lands his ship Twilight Heart at the Tatooine palace of the Hutt crime lord Juuka, met by the wary Devaronian majordomo Viszla. Led through the labyrinthine palace to the audience chamber, Vidious flatters Juuka on reclaiming the Desilijic throne while subtly probing and manipulating the slug's pride and avarice. He proposes a galaxy-spanning crime cartel to bring order to the chaotic underworld, sweetening the pitch by spilling a fortune in Corsuca gems across the floor as a down payment. Vidious points Juuka toward Corellia, where the Republic refits its fleet with smuggled arms ripe for exploitation, hinting darkly at the vast resources backing him without confirming his identity. Intrigued and greedy, Juuka accepts the tribute and agrees to act once his own sources verify the opportunity.",
